  <brief_title>Evaluate the Safety and Diagnostic Advantages of Tilt Down Verses Standard Horizontal Colonoscopy Positioning</brief_title>
  <acronym>CTDTTIE</acronym>
  <official_title>The Effect of Body Positioning for Colonoscopy in Women: Randomized, Study of Left Lateral Tilt Down Versus Left Lateral Horizontal Positioning</official_title>
  <sponsors>
